  <p>Environmental sustainability, chemical and plant efficiency, and product quality are essential elements in phosphoric acid production. <strong>JAS Global Industries</strong> addresses these factors head-on to provide you with a wide range of formulations to ensure all of these priorities are not only met but exceed your expectations.</p>
  <p>We ensure that you comply with the increasingly complex environmental regulations, but at the same time, step up the game to ensure your production process is as sustainable as can be. From controlling exhaust gases, to eliminating visual emissions, to disposing of contaminated wastewater safely, we ensure you are adequately prepared to meet these regulations. As environmental sustainability is increasingly prioritized, we have adapted our defoamer formulations to meet these requirements in the most sustainable way. Our product range will lower reactor levels, reduce foam that can damage equipment, and eliminate reactor overflows, ensuring you are adequately prepared for sustainable production.</p>
  <p>The presence of mineral impurities and dissolved gases can interfere with the chemical reactions that ensure you have high-quality phosphate deposits. Our defoamers significantly reduce these interferences to ensure proper crystal formulation and growth. Not only do we have defoamers to ensure you achieve chemical efficiency, but we also provide filtration aids that improve plant productivity. Phosphoric acid production plants need to vacuum filter sufficient amounts of acid to boost production rates, and with our filtration aids, you are guaranteed long-term effectiveness of your filtration system. With this in mind, we work with you to ensure that both your chemical efficiency and plant production rates are working hand-in-hand to provide you with optimal results.</p>
  <p>Finally, impurity levels of phosphoric acid must be low in order to meet the expectations for the production of concentrated fertilizers. While this can be difficult to achieve for some, our clarifying aids are more than effective at improving acid quality. With our aids, the settling and removal rates of impurities are significantly improved, which will ensure you produce an optimal product for the production of top-of-the-line fertilizers.</p>
