  <p>We provide refinery operators with a full range of products that help improve productivity and reduce operating costs, while prioritizing safety, health, and the environment. With our formulation expertise, modelling capabilities, and application knowledge, we partner with you to achieve greater profitability with a reduced environmental footprint. We deliver elite technical solutions to ensure mining operations are optimized to your advantage. </p>
  <p>F-Strike® is our range of multi-purpose defoamers that include dispersions, oils, and silicon and organic emulsions.</p>
